  "texts": [
    "As GPT-4 generates new output every time it is used, it is impossible for another researcher to replicate our findings.",
    "Additionally, due to the \"black box\" nature of LLMs (Roa & Biller-Andorno, 2023), it impossible to know what the processes or rationale were used by GPT-4 to generate the output that we obtain.",
    "However, to increase transparency, we have provided video recordings of our text generation which can be accessed here.",
    "identified in this study.",
    "Improving the citation and substantiation abilities of AI models will enhance the credibility and reliability of generated content."
  ]
